  <brief_title>Imaging of Prostate Cancer Using Two-Dimensional MR Spectroscopy and Diffusion Tensor Imaging</brief_title>
  <official_title>Imaging of Prostate Cancer Using Two-Dimensional MR Spectroscopy and Diffusion Tensor Imaging</official_title>
