  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal is to develop MR imaging techniques to improve delineation of cancer extent, and to
      improve differential diagnosis between prostate cancer and benign prostate hyperplasia or
      other benign diseases.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
